title: Catholic Comics {1946-49 - Golden Age}
description:
Included are 25 of the 28 issues published. If you have any of the missing 3, please upload them!


Catholic Comics was put out by Catholic Comics, Inc. Catholic Comics feature a variety of subjects, including sports stories with Bill Brown of Notre Dame (included in every issue), Father O'Malley and Pudgey Pig. They also have stories about science and religion, as well as some of Aesop's fables and Robert Louis Stevenson's Treasure Island broken down into a ten part series.
